Milwaukee.WVTV: WVTV, virtual and UHF digital channel 18, is a CW-affiliated television station licensed to Milwaukee, Wisconsin, United States. The station is owned by the Sinclair Broadcast Group. WVTV's studios are located on Calumet Road in the Park Place office park near the I-41/U.S. 45 interchange on Milwaukee's northwest side; its transmitter is located on North Humboldt Boulevard in Milwaukee's Estabrook Park neighborhood as part of the Milwaukee PBS tower.
